http://bmj.bmjjournals.com/cgi/content/full/331/7531/1498?ehom\">\"The case of the disappearing teaspoons\"</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tuppenceworth.ie/Politics/Corrib-5.html\">An application of Resistentalism to complex systems</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.org/details/OTRR_X_Minus_One_Singles\">X Minus One, 1950s radio show, episode 10: \"Nightmare\"</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://allpoetry.com/poem/8513591-Nightmare_Number_Three-by-Stephen_Vincent_Benet\">Nightmare Number 3, poem by Stephen Vincent Benet</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2224\nCached time: 20180913170217\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.088 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.120 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 215/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 3136/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 79/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 2836/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.037/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.53 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   97.497      1 -total\n 53.84%   52.488      1 Template:Reflist\n 42.06%   41.007      1 Template:About\n 37.76%   36.812      1 Template:Citation\n  3.05%    2.977      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:886839-0!canonical and timestamp 20180913170217 and revision id 856055848\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[{"lang":"da","url":"https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resistentialisme","langname":"Danish","autonym":"dansk","*":"Resistentialisme"},{"lang":"de","url":"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resistentialismus","langname":"German","autonym":"Deutsch","*":"Resistentia